Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Melt - minimal object-oriented programming language
 Melt is a minimal, interpreted, object-oriented language built in C++.
 It supports variables, classes, methods, control flow, file I/O, JSON,
 HTTP server, and optional MySQL/SQLite and loadable extensions.
 .
 Run: melt script.melt
